{"tid":142422,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老搭地鐵霸兩個位","createTime":"2017-03-03T17:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T17:31:54.000Z","uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"93d3e3bbcbba069c94f909aaf0053c531a06f8d4","tid":142422,"uid":36310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:29:48.000Z","msg":"俾得果兩蚊雞都好意思霸兩個位<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9y7c5mds\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9y7c5mds&h=e2a09bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然夜晚人唔算多<br />\n但都有人企係佢前面等<br />\n當有人行過去懶好心咁將個袋貼埋側邊<br />\n係貼埋側邊唔係攬係前面<br />\n擺明唔想人坐<br />\n到左下個站<br />\n有個啊叔衝入黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1hyfujb7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1hyfujb7&h=0c873999&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n乜都冇講就咁坐落去<br />\n個啊婆9秒9拎起個袋<br />\n結論:啊婆動作其實好撚敏捷 只係扮慘唔想俾你地坐"},{"pid":"ed4a0d197caa68db3296f25f9755353f602e921e","tid":142422,"uid":17497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"d廢老個撚個都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但廢老又治返廢老<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}